the intelligent system experience


6
00:00:18,485 --> 00:00:21,255 line:-1
provides a lot of value for the developer.


7
00:00:21,321 --> 00:00:23,557 line:-2
Now, we'll look
at how this benefits users.


8
00:00:24,091 --> 00:00:26,727 line:-2
To do this, let's walk
through how system intelligence


9
00:00:26,793 --> 00:00:30,297 line:-2
can actually help people,
