checking the app frequently enough.


76
00:03:54,268 --> 00:03:56,436 line:-1
Luckily, this year, with the new widgets,


77
00:03:56,503 --> 00:04:00,274 line:-2
there's an intelligent experience
available right on her Home Screen.


78
00:04:01,141 --> 00:04:02,409 line:-1
With a few quick taps,


79
00:04:02,476 --> 00:04:05,345 line:-2
she can create a Smart Stack
with all her favorite widgets,


80
00:04:05,412 --> 00:04:08,448 line:-2
including Mission Gym,
and add it to her Home Screen.


81
00:04:09,049 --> 00:04:13,053 line:-2
Thanks to system intelligence,
the stack will rotate automatically


82
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:16,423 line:-2
to show the most relevant
and timely widget.


83
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:19,760 line:-2
So, in her case,
if the class schedule changes,


84
00:04:19,826 --> 00:04:22,796 line:-2
the stack will automatically rotate
to the gym widget,


85
00:04:22,863 --> 00:04:25,899 line:-2
giving her enough time
to react to any changes.


86
00:04:25,966 --> 00:04:28,101 line:-1
This way she'll never miss a class.


87
00:04:28,502 --> 00:04:30,170 line:-1
More importantly, in the future,


88
00:04:30,237 --> 00:04:33,273 line:-2
she can browse upcoming class times
directly on her Home Screen


89
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:36,810 line:-2
by glancing at the widget
and picking a time that works for her.


90
00:04:36,877 --> 00:04:38,512 line:-1
If she wants to learn more,


91
00:04:38,579 --> 00:04:42,182 line:-2
she can always tap on the widget
to jump to the right place in the app.


92
00:04:42,249 --> 00:04:45,552 line:-2
So instead of looking for the app
and then navigating through it,


93
00:04:45,619 --> 00:04:48,288 line:-2
she can find everything
right on her Home Screen.


94
00:04:49,022 --> 00:04:52,192 line:-2
Our friend has been working out
pretty frequently now.


95
00:04:52,259 --> 00:04:55,829 line:-2
She did notice, however,
she has been repeating the same few things


96
00:04:55,896 --> 00:04:57,531 line:-1
